===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|boton}} (French {{term|bouton}}), itself either from {{etyl|LL.}} *{{term||bottōnem}}, probably ultimately from a {{etyl|gem}} language, or from {{term|bouter|lang=fr}} + {{term|-on|lang=fr}}.

[[Image:Brownell's trouser button.jpg|thumb|right|150px|Shirt button (sense 1)]]
[[Image:Enter_button.jpg|thumb|right|150px|Push button (sense 2)]]

